in the Baishi Road car accident.

56
00:04:17,450 --> 00:04:18,890
Come with us for investigation.

57
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:29,210
Are you Ma Haoda?

58
00:04:30,330 --> 00:04:30,940
Yes, that's me.

59
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:31,750
What's going on?

60
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:32,690
Come with us.

61
00:04:32,690 --> 00:04:33,990
Cooperate with the investigation.

62
